# Frontend Development Rules

## Related Documentation

- [Architecture](../docs/ARCHITECTURE.md) - Full technology stack, directory structure, and patterns
- [Frontend Improvements](../docs/FRONTEND_IMPROVEMENTS.md) - Known issues and planned improvements
- [README](../README.md) - Quick start and domain concepts

## Technology Stack

- **Framework**: React 19 (functional components only)
- **UI Library**: Mantine 8 (migrating from MUI/Emotion — do NOT use MUI for new code)
- **Styling**: Mantine style props + `style` prop; Emotion only for custom breakpoints/pseudo-elements
- **State Management**: Zustand 5 (preferred), Bacon.js for reactive streams (legacy)
- **Routing**: React Router 7
- **Build Tool**: Vite 7
- **Date Handling**: Luxon
- **Validation**: Zod 4
- **Icons**: Lucide React (`lucide-react`) via `src/client/ui/icons/Icons.tsx`

